# CONSYS Stage W1 spike (Phase 8 WiFi, Gate G2a — plan.md "WiFi plan"
# Stage 2, activated 2026-07-14 with B-19 parked).
#
# MTK_PMIC_WRAP: mainline pwrap, mt6797 + mt6351 slave both supported
# upstream; first PMIC access from Linux in this project (LK inits the
# wrapper, driver re-init is a checked no-op).
# REGULATOR_MT6351: minimal VCN-rails-only driver
# (patches/v6.6/regulator/0002).
# MTK_CONSYS_SPIKE: throwaway Gate-G2a probe driver
# (patches/v6.6/soc/0003) — powers VCN18/VCN28 + CONN MTCMOS
# (patches/v6.6/pmdomain/0002) and polls the CONSYS chip ID (expect
# 0x0279); pass/fail is a single dmesg line ("GATE G2A PASS"/"FAIL").
CONFIG_MTK_PMIC_WRAP=y
CONFIG_REGULATOR_MT6351=y
CONFIG_MTK_CONSYS_SPIKE=y
